{"tid":463273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女高中生遭男友曝光裸照　閨蜜竟補刀傳閱","createTime":"2017-11-09T10:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T11:53:07.000Z","uid":71094,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d5ee5d7dec399207f8a239cf054ab9ab1be5529d","tid":463273,"uid":71094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:35:32.000Z","msg":"2017/11/09 15:53<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;（更新：新增動新聞）雲林某高中日前傳出女學生裸照流出風波，引發學生議論紛紛，雖沒看過裸照，但都知道當事人姓名。校長證實確有裸照事件，指全案是二年級一名女生，收到同班被害女學生男友傳來的被害女生裸照後，用手機秀出照片給其他男女同學看，消息因而傳開，被害女學生獲知後求助爸媽，校方已請雙方學生與家長對談，並當場刪除手機內照片。<br />\n<br />\n校長說，兩名女主角在師長眼中算好朋友，之前還會幫買早餐，互動良好，也沒有兩人起衝突的傳聞，訝異竟會秀閨蜜裸照給別人看。而經校方調查，事件中3男女都相識，秀照片女學生先結識校外的男方，介紹給被害女認識並交往，男方則回頭向她炫耀有被害女裸照並傳送，而被拿出來給其他同學看。校方指已啟動校安通報，將釐清多少人涉入，會加強輔導、保護被害學生，輔導其他參與學生，但也呼籲同學若與異性交往，千萬別自拍裸照表達愛，一旦外流，內心創傷難以想像。但校方表示，學校調查之餘，還不了解拍裸照原因，與男友為何傳出女友裸照，但將請被害學生家長找女兒男友溝通，請對方刪除照片，杜絕再度外洩可能。而雲林縣警察局婦幼隊表示，《兒童及少年性剝削防制條例》第 36 條，拍攝、製造兒童或少年為性交或猥褻行為之圖畫、照片、影片、影帶、光碟、電子訊號或其他物品，處6個月以上5年以下有期徒刑，得併科新臺幣50萬元以下罰金，警方將介入了解偵辦。（林靜盛、李政遠／雲林報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女人同女人之間真係好陰濕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20171109/1237076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20171109%2F1237076&d=qFMizAWkK58qCn8pkwBdHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cc776242\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20171109%2F1237076&h=eb9082b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20171109/1237076</a>"},{"pid":"a0ac3e2767930e5119b02ab47160b8ccb4c36573","tid":463273,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:36:10.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"df884477d4ba16ad09e3894485295eff5b90c61f","tid":463273,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958c37e82a81d337407ce7202a9ccd8d4a9cd0c0","tid":463273,"uid":103879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"永遠冇三登份"},{"pid":"7b9fbabfc6625189d48f80b74886b70bdd65984a","tid":463273,"uid":41515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"又無連登份"},{"pid":"28c9a1c76811df1271fbb554a239a9b41edc9518","tid":463273,"uid":22566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"圖都冇 呢篇新聞仲有咩價值"},{"pid":"af1379438dad25b3f6bfaacd0841a37d4838530e","tid":463273,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:37:34.000Z","msg":"雲林+5分<br />\n台仔number one<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f2aa513192e7ca3edcfbbbff9a79ab5cd63a28","tid":463273,"uid":69429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:39:05.000Z","msg":"擺明係鐘意個男既 比人搶左咪報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca30ce36704ebc9414fc3c9c7b28ad5b0bbd35af","tid":463273,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"網上瘋傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fdd02082db3c258c39b5f75ce4b33f11c052ba4","tid":463273,"uid":70227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/09/195304_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-sr